# README‑snippets.mdc

### Show a notification

```js
chrome.notifications.create({
  type: 'basic',
  iconUrl: 'assets/icon48.png',
  title: 'Time for Dhikr',
  message: 'سُبْحَانَ اللَّهِ',
});
```

### Schedule hourly alarms

```js
chrome.alarms.create('dhikr‑tick', { periodInMinutes: 60 });
```

### Continue audio after popup closes

```js
if (!await chrome.offscreen.hasDocument()) {
  await chrome.offscreen.createDocument({
    url: 'offscreen.html',
    reasons: ['AUDIO_PLAYBACK'],
    justification: 'Keep Qur’an audio playing',
  });
}
```

